---
title: Mexican Smashed Chickpea & Garlic Rice with Toasted Pumpkin Seeds & Pickled Onion Salsa
description: Don’t be fooled by the ‘smashed’ in our Mexican smashed chickpea bowl, this dish is tranquil and easy, perfect for any hectic weekday night. Soothing rice soaks up an ensemble of tastes from the pickled onion, spiced chickpeas and toasted pumpkin seeds. So don’t worry, you can sit back and relax into dinner tonight.
